### Step 3

Coordinate Compression

Unique values

```
[-1,0,1]
```

Ranks

```
-1 → 1
 0 → 2
 1 → 3
```

---

### Step 4

Process Prefixes

| Current Prefix | Rank | Previous Smaller Prefixes | Added Answer | Total |
| -------------- | ---- | ------------------------- | ------------ | ----- |
| 0              | 2    | 0                         | 0            | 0     |
| -1             | 1    | 0                         | 0            | 0     |
| 0              | 2    | -1                        | 1            | 1     |
| 1              | 3    | -1,0,0                    | 3            | 4     |
| 0              | 2    | -1                        | 1            | 5     |

Answer

```
5
```

